name: BOEING FACTORY PLANE SPOTTING! Everett Paine Field (PAE/KPAE) [4K]
description:
The day I filmed the NASA DC-8 at Paine Field in Everett, Washington, there were a few other movements of interest, including multiple KC-46 test flights, a 747 LCF Dreamlifter departing for Charleston, South Carolina, and a rare Boeing 737-600 from the secretive Janet Airlines.

I've compiled them all into this 18 minute video, so I hope you enjoy!
